channel.title: How to fix problem with compiler![tut. for newbies]
channel.description:
okay thats my first tutorial! so let's start. very often peoples have that problem.you changed something in server but when you click compile to fix that what you changed,pop up a window and there is any error!like not right java or something else. to not download a correct java,i know a way how to fix the compiler.first of all go to "start" at your desktop then "run" there write cmd a black window will pop up write there java - version it load up and gives you your java version,mine java version is 1.6.0_21 ok,then go to your cource and find out your compiler.then right mouse click on it and press "change" a text document will pop up.there find the java version and change it to your.save it.close.
and cratz you now got a working compiler.enjoy changing your server! :D
